metadata.name: CryptoSerg #1
metadata.description:
Serg stories:  
[CryptoSerg #842](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/842), [CryptoSerg #191](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/191), and [CryptoSerg #1](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/1) came to the wax museum. [CryptoSerg #1](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/1) played peepers with figures.
  
[CryptoSerg #1](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/1), [CryptoSerg #949](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/949) and [CryptoSerg #157](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/157) have arrived at the cottage. The guys wanted to rest, but [CryptoSerg #1](https://opensea.io/assets/0x18Ed5803cD47F91716E06E38216e211ffAa9cC07/1) made them pull out the grass and plant potatoes.
